      <t>&lt;p&gt;This specification extends the Post Office Protocol version 3 (POP3) to support un-encoded international characters in user names, passwords, mail addresses, message headers, and protocol-level textual error strings.  This document defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
